Aug 20 (Reuters) - The following financial services industry appointments were announced on Wednesday. To inform us of other job changes, email moves@thomsonreuters.com.

RBC GLOBAL ASSET MANAGEMENT The unit of Royal Bank of Canada <RY.TO> appointed Clive Brown CEO and managing director of its international business. Brown joins from JP Morgan Asset Management, where he was global chief operating officer and chairman of Asia, based in Hong Kong. [ID:nL4N0QQ2UY]  DIFC AUTHORITY